properties.name: management.endpoint.nacos-discovery.cache.time-to-live
properties.description: Maximum time that a response can be cached.

properties.name: management.endpoint.nacos-discovery.enabled
properties.description: Whether to enable the nacos-discovery endpoint.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.access-key
properties.description: access key for namespace.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.cluster-name
properties.description: cluster name for nacos .

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.enabled
properties.description: enable nacos discovery or not.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.endpoint
properties.description: the domain name of a service, through which the server address can be dynamically obtained.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.group
properties.description: group name for nacos.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.heart-beat-interval
properties.description: Heart beat interval. Time unit: second.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.heart-beat-timeout
properties.description: Heart beat timeout. Time unit: second.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.ip
properties.description: The ip address your want to register for your service instance, needn't to set it if the auto detect ip works well.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.ip-delete-timeout
properties.description: Ip delete timeout. Time unit: second.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.log-name
properties.description: nacos naming log file name.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.metadata
properties.description: extra metadata to register.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.namespace
properties.description: namespace, separation registry of different environments.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.naming-load-cache-at-start
properties.description: naming load from local cache at application start. true is load.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.namingLoadCacheAtStart
properties.description: naming load from local cache at application start .

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.network-interface
properties.description: which network interface's ip you want to register.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.port
properties.description: The port your want to register for your service instance, needn't to set it if the auto detect port works well.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.register-enabled
properties.description: if you just want to subscribe, but don't want to register your service, set it to false.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.secret-key
properties.description: secret key for namespace.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.secure
properties.description: whether your service is a https service.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.server-addr
properties.description: nacos discovery server address.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.service
properties.description: the service name to register, default value is ${spring.application.name}.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.watch-delay
properties.description: watch delay,duration to pull new service from nacos server.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.watch.enabled
properties.description: enable nacos discovery watch or not .

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.discovery.weight
properties.description: weight for service instance, the larger the value, the larger the weight.

properties.name: spring.cloud.nacos.server-addr
properties.description: nacos server address.
